SUMMARY:NAHJ Student Summit 2026
DESCRIPTION:Join us this spring for the NAHJ Student Summit\, a full-day experience designed to inform\, inspire\, and connect the next generation of journalists. Hosted by the NAHJ Student Chapter of UCF\, this summit will bring together students for engaging conversations\, skill-building sessions\, and opportunities to network with peers and professionals. \n🗓 Saturday\, April 18\, 2026\n⏰ 8:30 a.m. – 4:00 p.m.\n📍 Nicholson School of Communication and Media\n12405 Aquarius Agora Dr\, Orlando\, FL 32816 \n🎟 Free for students\n✅ Pre-registration required\n🔗 Register here \nWhether you’re just starting out or preparing to enter the industry\, this summit is a great chance to learn\, connect\, and grow within the NAHJ community.
URL:https://nahj.org/event/nahj-student-summit-2026/
LOCATION:Orlando\, Florida\, Nicholson School of Communication and Media\, 12405 Aquarius Agora Dr.\, Orlando\, FL\, 32816\, United States
CATEGORIES:Next Generation
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://nahj.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Student-Summit-2026.jpg
END:VEVENT
