SUMMARY:Digital Open-Source Investigations: Chronolocation Webinar
DESCRIPTION:An NAHJ webinar training series for 2026: Digital Open-Source Investigations and OSINT for Journalism\n\nChronolocation \nParticipants will learn how to verify images and videos by finding approximately when they were recorded using geolocation\, sunlight\, and shadows. \nWhen: Tuesday\, May 12\, 2026\nTime: 6:00 PM – 7:15 PM EST\nRegister: https://nahj.memberclicks.net/OSINTchrono \nPresented by: OSINT Reporting Lab at USC Annenberg School for Communication and Journalism  \n  \n 
URL:https://nahj.org/event/digital-open-source-investigations-chronolocation-webinar/
